{"tid":644462,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"55歲湯告魯斯搏到盡 為拍戲跳傘106次","createTime":"2018-04-27T08:54:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-27T08:55:42.000Z","uid":41343,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0bce23da65b600ab233f42da5d9a3316273d550d","tid":644462,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T08:54:45.000Z","msg":"荷里活巨星湯告魯斯主演的《職業特工隊：叛逆之謎》將於今年暑假上映，近日他與拍檔西蒙柏奇、導演Christopher McQuarrie等人出席電影博覽會，現場播出湯告魯斯跳傘一幕。原來他從頭到尾沒有用替身，為拍攝完美角度，湯告魯斯跳傘106次，令人佩服，導演更稱讚湯告魯斯是「可以做到的事比你要他做的來得更多」。<br />\n<br />\n55歲的湯告魯斯相當敬業，盡力親自上陣拍動作戲，更獲得本年度電影博覽會的年度先鋒獎。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.singtao.ca/toronto/wp-content/uploads/master_sandbox/2018/04/wpid-2018042712422485330.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.singtao.ca%2Ftoronto%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fmaster_sandbox%2F2018%2F04%2Fwpid-2018042712422485330.jpg&h=848b07f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.singtao.ca/toronto/2534874/2018-04-27/post-湯告魯斯搏到盡-為拍戲跳傘106次/?variant=zh-hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.singtao.ca%2Ftoronto%2F2534874%2F2018-04-27%2Fpost-%E6%B9%AF%E5%91%8A%E9%AD%AF%E6%96%AF%E6%90%8F%E5%88%B0%E7%9B%A1-%E7%82%BA%E6%8B%8D%E6%88%B2%E8%B7%B3%E5%82%98106%E6%AC%A1%2F%3Fvariant%3Dzh-hk&d=ZYVhrGFvApibtd1c5U7j4TA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=d580ce16\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.singtao.ca/toronto/2534874/2018-04-27/post-湯告魯斯搏到盡-為拍戲跳傘106次/?variant=zh-hk</a>"},{"pid":"0948416c60c27895186755b4010cf61dc1c4b2b3","tid":644462,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T08:55:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}